# FILE: serviceCatalog.desc
# ROLE: Category Deep-Dive & Service Exploration
# VIBE: Industrial Directory / Grid-Heavy / Filter-Focus

## 1. DYNAMIC CATEGORY HEADER (Top 20%)
- **VISUAL:** Large, blurred background image matching the selected "Main Disciplinary" (e.g., Code/Architecture).
- **TITLE:** [ 💻 البرمجيات والتطوير ] (Software & Development).
- **SUB-TITLE:** "Browse specialized services from top-tier student developers."
- **BREADCRUMBS:** Home > Freelance > Software.

## 2. ADVANCED FILTER TERMINAL (Left Sidebar/Top Bar)
- **SEARCH FIELD:** "Search within this category..." (e.g., "React", "Python").
- **SERVICE LEVEL:** [ 🥉 Junior ] | [ 🥈 Pro ] | [ 🥇 Elite ].
- **PRICE FILTER:** Minimum to Maximum SYP Slider.
- **DELIVERY TIME:** [ ⚡ Fast (24h) ] | [ 🕒 Standard ] | [ 🗓️ Custom ].
- **SORTING:** "Highest Rated" | "Lowest Price" | "Newest Additions".

## 3. THE SERVICE GRID (Main Area)
- **LAYOUT:** 3-column grid of detailed service cards.
- **SERVICE CARD DATA:**
    - **IMAGE:** Cover image of the specific service (e.g., a website screenshot).
    - **FREELANCER SNIPPET:** Small avatar + Name + **[ ✅ Verified ]**.
    - **TITLE:** "I will build a professional MERN stack dashboard for your project."
    - **PRICING:** Starting from **150,000 SYP**.
    - **STATS:** [ ⭐ 5.0 (12 Reviews) ] | [ 📦 3 Orders in Queue ].

## 4. THE "PROMOTED SERVICE" SLOT (Top Row)
- **LOGIC:** The first 2 spots in the grid are "Featured" (Admin-controlled or highest rating).
- **STYLE:** Subtle glowing border (Cyan/Purple) to highlight top-tier quality.

## 5. THE SERVICE LIGHTBOX (Quick View)
- **INTERACTION:** Clicking a card opens a popup before the full subpage.
- **DETAILS:** - **Included:** 3 Revisions, Source Code, Documentation.
    - **Duration:** 5 Days.
- **ACTION:** [ 💳 اطلب الآن ] | [ 💬 استفسار ] (Direct Message).

## 6. CATEGORY FOOTER (The "Can't Find It?" Node)
- **MESSAGE:** "Looking for something custom that isn't listed here?"
- **PRIMARY CTA:** **[ 📝 انشر طلبك الخاص - Post a Custom Task ]**
- **LOGIC:** Redirects to a form where freelancers can bid on the client's specific needs.

